### THE MOVIE PREDICTOR ###
version 1.0

# WHAT IS IT ?

This app will predict the rating of a newly released movie, based on his multiple features.
features can be for exemple marketing budget, release date, actors, directors, duration, ranking...

# HOW DOES IT WORK ?

The app compare a new movie to a large database based on the OMDB database.
The app updates his database every wednesday, to make sure no movies are forgotten.
Finally, the IA model included in the app will process the chosen movie with the large database and will predict his rating.

# COMMANDS

After reading the README and identify yourself with the .env file, please run the following command to add a random movie to the database.

$ docker-compose up --build


